      "text": "[[Responsive Web Design]] is an approach to web design aimed at crafting sites to provide an optimal viewing and interaction experience—easy reading and navigation with a minimum of resizing, panning, and scrolling—across a wide range of devices (from desktop computer monitors to mobile phones) - [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Responsive_web_design wikipedia]\n\n"
